text: On this 16-century chart of Goes, "Zeer Henriks kinderen" appears in the bottom left corner. ‌'s-Heer Hendrikskinderen is a village in the Dutch province of Zeeland. It is located in the municipality of Goes, about 2 km to the west of the city of Goes. 's-Heer Hendrikskinderen was a separate municipality until 1857. ==References== Category:Populated places in Zeeland Category:Former municipalities of Zeeland Category:Goes
title: 's-Heer Hendrikskinderen
